item.dc:creator: @K4rn4ge K4rn4ge
item.description:
@K4rn4ge wrote:

I’ve Never used a 525 b4 but are you using a 525 client? or the client that came with it?

Or change ip in these

GUI.java
EGUI.java
Client.java

(those are all in the client folder… and you only need one of the GUI’s)

(so if you got EGUI you shouldnt have GUI)

Hope that helps

item.title: Run Server, batch HELP
item.dc:creator: @johno2 johno2
item.description:
@johno2 wrote:

Basically, it’s just telling you whats loaded up.

The problem with; error_game_js5connect (This is what i think) It’s trying to read a different IP Then what your JC-Scape server uses to run,

So i would recommend going though your source/client and make sure that every ip is the same.

I’m sorry, but this is the most help i can give because ive never used 503+

~Johno
